<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 16:08:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“阿维胡在加沙”：进入加沙并被以色列国防军误杀的以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/avihu-is-in-gaza-the-israeli-who-entered-gaza-and-was-mistakenly-killed-by-the-idf/0000018d-0d91-de9c-a3df-6ff9998f0000</link><description>数百名恐怖分子越过边境围栏屠杀平民两周后，29 岁的阿维胡·莫里 (Avihu Mori) 畅通无阻地步行半公里进入加沙，直到被以色列国防军杀害。两个月后，他的家人仍在等待这位前士兵如何越过边境围栏的答案</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 15:51:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/avihu-is-in-gaza-the-israeli-who-entered-gaza-and-was-mistakenly-killed-by-the-idf/0000018d-0d91-de9c-a3df-6ff9998f0000</guid></item><item><title>因 Instagram 故事而被拘留的阿拉伯裔以色列记者被软禁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-journalist-detained-for-instagram-story-released-to-house-arrest/0000018d-0cee-db13-affd-7def48b90000</link><description>塔里克·塔哈 (Tareq Taha) 是阿拉伯新闻“Arab 48”的编辑，也是海法理工大学的学生，因在武装以色列学生的照片上张贴巴勒斯坦国旗而被捕。他的律师说，“他反对伤害犹太人和巴勒斯坦人，并不是每个帖子都是煽动的”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 15:40:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-journalist-detained-for-instagram-story-released-to-house-arrest/0000018d-0cee-db13-affd-7def48b90000</guid></item><item><title>随着爱荷华州预选会议的开始，共和党候选人尼基·哈利 (Nikki Haley) 和罗恩·德桑蒂斯 (Ron DeSantis) 将以色列和加沙作为大棒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-iowa-caucuses-kick-off-gop-candidates-haley-desantis-use-israel-and-gaza-as-a-cudgel/0000018d-0cde-d71c-ad9f-4fded9040000</link><description>两位共和党总统候选人正在争夺仅次于领先者特朗普的第二名 — — 在共和党寻求巩固其亲以色列立场之际，他们将以色列和反犹太主义武器化，以包抄对方</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 15:34:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-iowa-caucuses-kick-off-gop-candidates-haley-desantis-use-israel-and-gaza-as-a-cudgel/0000018d-0cde-d71c-ad9f-4fded9040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须保护亚美尼亚基督徒免受耶路撒冷袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-protect-armenians-christians-from-attacks-in-jerusalem/0000018d-0c1d-daa5-a7cf-de7f08cd0000</link><description>亚美尼亚前总统：在耶路撒冷老城，世界上最古老的亚美尼亚侨民社区的所在地，土地纠纷中爆发了暴力事件，可能威胁到亚美尼亚区的未来。我们要求以色列当局立即干预</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 15:05:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-protect-armenians-christians-from-attacks-in-jerusalem/0000018d-0c1d-daa5-a7cf-de7f08cd0000</guid></item><item><title>“没有地方是安全的”：加沙的医生“住在手术室里”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nowhere-is-safe-doctors-in-gaza-live-in-operating-room/0000018d-0c86-d71c-ad9f-4f861a230000</link><description>与其他战区和灾区不同，加沙地带的非政府组织医务人员在拯救生命的过程中冒着生命危险。一名员工描述了医生跪在地板上照顾伤员和数千名在医院避难的流离失所者的情况</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:51:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/nowhere-is-safe-doctors-in-gaza-live-in-operating-room/0000018d-0c86-d71c-ad9f-4f861a230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部城市拉阿纳纳发生恐怖袭击 妇女死亡 17 人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/at-least-19-wounded-in-ramming-and-stabbing-in-central-israeli-city-of-raanana/0000018d-0cf3-db13-affd-7df707d80000</link><description>据紧急服务部门称，包括一名 16 岁男孩在内的 3 人伤势严重，包括 6 名儿童在内的 14 人轻伤至中度受伤</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 12:29:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/at-least-19-wounded-in-ramming-and-stabbing-in-central-israeli-city-of-raanana/0000018d-0cf3-db13-affd-7df707d80000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日之后，这座以色列城市变成了一座鬼城。它的居民还能回家吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/is-there-hope-for-israeli-city-turned-ghost-town-after-october-7/0000018d-0741-dd94-a9cd-47ed08780000</link><description>位于以色列与加沙地带边境的斯德洛特是 10 月 7 日受灾最严重的城市。市长阿隆·戴维迪现在表示：“如果一百万加沙人返回加沙地带北部，那就是一次失败”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 11:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/is-there-hope-for-israeli-city-turned-ghost-town-after-october-7/0000018d-0741-dd94-a9cd-47ed08780000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯公布三名以色列人在加沙被扣为人质的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/hamas-releases-video-of-three-israelis-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018d-0c29-d71c-ad9f-4fab2b520000</link><description>视频发布后不久，美国总统乔·拜登发表声明，纪念加沙人质被关押100天：“我再次向所有人质及其家人重申我的承诺——我们与你们同在”</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 10:34:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/hamas-releases-video-of-three-israelis-held-hostage-in-gaza/0000018d-0c29-d71c-ad9f-4fab2b520000</guid></item><item><title>以色列足球运动员被土耳其当局释放，预计将返回以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/israeli-soccer-player-arrested-in-turkey-for-celebrating-goal-with-tribute-to-hostages/0000018d-0c0f-d71c-ad9f-4f8f416e0000</link><description>萨吉夫·耶赫兹克尔 (Sagiv Yehezkhel) 在庆祝进球并向在加沙被扣为人质的以色列人致敬后被拘留审讯</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 07:48:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/israeli-soccer-player-arrested-in-turkey-for-celebrating-goal-with-tribute-to-hostages/0000018d-0c0f-d71c-ad9f-4f8f416e0000</guid></item><item><title>释放人质的代价是以色列政府承认失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/the-price-of-freeing-hostages-admitting-the-war-has-failed/0000018d-0958-d71c-ad9f-4bdaac800000</link><description>在新一轮人质协议谈判中，哈马斯的要求似乎比上一次协议高出几乎无法估量。 ■ 同意这些要求将意味着结束与以色列的战争，而以色列未能实现击败哈马斯并削弱其能力的目标</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 04:41:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/the-price-of-freeing-hostages-admitting-the-war-has-failed/0000018d-0958-d71c-ad9f-4bdaac800000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队从加沙地带战斗中撤出战斗师；也门机场附近传来爆炸声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-live/hamas-releases-video-of-three-israeli-hostages/0000018d-0af5-d71c-ad9f-4bf75d0b0000</link><description>以色列国防军将战斗师从加沙地带撤出战斗 ■ 也门荷台达机场附近传来爆炸声 ■ 英国海事机构收到报告称，也门亚丁海岸附近的船只遭到导弹袭击 ■ 以色列中部城市拉&amp;#39;发生恐怖袭击，造成一名妇女死亡、14 人受伤anana ■ Shin Bet 揭露伊朗招募和动员以色列公民的网络</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 03:23:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article-live/hamas-releases-video-of-three-israeli-hostages/0000018d-0af5-d71c-ad9f-4bf75d0b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的精神卫生预算将被削减，而不是20亿谢克尔的补助</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-a-two-billion-shekel-supplement-israels-mental-health-budget-will-be-cut/0000018d-0a96-d71c-ad9f-4b963c6a0000</link><description>2024年国家预算将卫生部预算削减4亿谢克尔，而就在几周前，卫生部宣布了一项新的20亿谢克尔精神卫生计划</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 02:16:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/instead-of-a-two-billion-shekel-supplement-israels-mental-health-budget-will-be-cut/0000018d-0a96-d71c-ad9f-4b963c6a0000</guid></item><item><title>周日，五名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-soldiers-on-sunday-in-the-west-bank/0000018d-0a0e-d8a7-a1df-aebe2edb0000</link><description>自10月7日与哈马斯的战争开始以来，已有300多名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸与以色列安全部队的冲突中丧生</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 23:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/five-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-soldiers-on-sunday-in-the-west-bank/0000018d-0a0e-d8a7-a1df-aebe2edb0000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨和艾森科特探索“创造性”人质释放方案；内塔尼亚胡和加兰特坚持军事压力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/gantz-explores-creative-hostage-release-options-netanyahu-insists-on-military-pressure/0000018d-09d7-daa5-a7cf-dff7453b0000</link><description>中间派部长甘茨和艾森科特推动达成协议，释放加沙剩余人质，但内塔尼亚胡和加兰特警告不要在消灭哈马斯之前停火。与此同时，卡塔尔和埃及努力弥合与哈马斯谈判中的分歧</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 22:01:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-15/ty-article/.premium/gantz-explores-creative-hostage-release-options-netanyahu-insists-on-military-pressure/0000018d-09d7-daa5-a7cf-dff7453b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的战争已经过去 100 天了。武力不能继续是前进的唯一途径</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-war-marks-100-days-force-cannot-remain-the-only-way-forward/0000018d-09b6-daa5-a7cf-dff659030000</link><description>大多数以色列人相信，军事行动是唯一的出路，任何谈论谈判的巴勒斯坦人都被认为是妄想。需要真正的范式转变</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 21:17:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-war-marks-100-days-force-cannot-remain-the-only-way-forward/0000018d-09b6-daa5-a7cf-dff659030000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯被囚禁100天：以色列人质家属必须发动自己的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-14/ty-article/.highlight/100-days-in-hamas-captivity-israeli-hostages-families-must-wage-their-own-war/0000018d-08c1-daa5-a7cf-dee332850000</link><description>当仍被扣押在加沙的 136 名人质迎来被囚禁一百天之际，他们的亲属正在考虑必须继续战斗，谁知道他们的困境还要持续多久才能成为公众关注的焦点</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 18:04:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-01-14/ty-article/.highlight/100-days-in-hamas-captivity-israeli-hostages-families-must-wage-their-own-war/0000018d-08c1-daa5-a7cf-dee332850000</guid></item><item><title>战争爆发时，我们与这些加沙人进行了交谈。这就是他们所经历的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-talked-with-these-gazans-when-the-war-broke-this-is-where-they-are-now/0000018d-0870-d8a7-a1df-aefef6540000</link><description>《国土报》重新采访了四名加沙人，他们在战争刚开始时就谈到了战争，发现他们流离失所、遭到轰炸，挤在狭小的地区，同时努力寻求医疗救助，并感到死亡即将来临</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:56:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-talked-with-these-gazans-when-the-war-broke-this-is-where-they-are-now/0000018d-0870-d8a7-a1df-aefef6540000</guid></item><item><title>真主党导弹杀死以色列妇女及其儿子；以色列国防军击毙三名渗透黎巴嫩边境的恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-missile-kills-two-israelis-idf-kills-terrorists-infiltrating-lebanon-border/0000018d-0859-d8a7-a1df-aeffda470000</link><description>以色列军队称袭击了黎巴嫩真主党目标，并下令关闭边境地区的民用交通。 ■ 以色列国防军估计，渗透边境的恐怖分子计划袭击附近的一个基地；巴勒斯坦组织声称对此事负责</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:53:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-missile-kills-two-israelis-idf-kills-terrorists-infiltrating-lebanon-border/0000018d-0859-d8a7-a1df-aeffda470000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔的高级盟友和顾问因煽动种族主义而被定罪，恐怖指控被无罪释放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/top-ben-gvir-ally-and-adviser-convicted-of-inciting-racism-acquitted-of-terror-charges/0000018d-0841-d71c-ad9f-4bc314350000</link><description>极右翼卡汉主义者本茨·戈普斯坦因针对阿拉伯人的言论而被定罪：“我们内部的敌人是癌症。”他因发表美化 1994 年希伯伦大屠杀的种族主义言论而被无罪释放。判决后他说道：“我为我所说的话感到自豪”</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:51:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/.premium/top-ben-gvir-ally-and-adviser-convicted-of-inciting-racism-acquitted-of-terror-charges/0000018d-0841-d71c-ad9f-4bc314350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名周六在加沙地带战斗中丧生的以色列预备役士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-reserve-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-saturday/0000018d-0879-d71c-ad9f-4bfb1dcb0000</link><description>这名士兵的身份是安杜阿拉姆·卡巴达 (Andualem Kabada)，21 岁，来自南部城市加特 (Kiryat Gat)；军方报告称，另一名士兵在同一事件中受重伤</description><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jan 2024 15:43:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-14/ty-article/idf-names-israeli-reserve-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-fighting-on-saturday/0000018d-0879-d71c-ad9f-4bfb1dcb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>